fuckin hate your noname uploads

Since there are several movies named "Shooters", it would be nice to have a hint as to which one this is. Some people like to look at IMDB prior to taking the time to view a movie. And, specification of the language could save a bit of gnashing of teeth, when it turns out to be in South-East Marsian!
